segments.filteredText: Fortunately the language we all have in the browser. JavaScript doesn't have a mature suit of data science libraries and it's missing a number of features that are useful for numerical Computing such as operator. Overloading. We still think it's worthwhile to work on changing that and moving the JavaScript data science ecosystem forward. In the meantime. We are also taking a shortcut. We are meeting data scientists where they are by bringing the popular and mature python scientific stack to the browser.
